Sentencas: In this present work, La-10(SiO4)(6)O-3 as a promising electrolyte candidate for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs) has been synthesized and its electrical property was investigated as a function of temperature.
Titulo: Electrical Properties of Atmospheric Plasma-Sprayed La10(SiO4)6O3 Electrolyte Coatings

Sentencas: In order to improve the density and oxide ion conductivity of La-10(SiO4)(6)O-3, the feedstock powder was prepared by sintering the oxide mixture powders at proper sintering temperatures and times.
Titulo: Electrical Properties of Atmospheric Plasma-Sprayed La10(SiO4)6O3 Electrolyte Coatings

Sentencas: The hexagonal apatite-type ceramic coatings with a typical composition of La-10(SiO4)(6)O-3 were deposited by atmospheric plasma spraying (APS) with different hydrogen flow rates.
Titulo: Electrical Properties of Atmospheric Plasma-Sprayed La10(SiO4)6O3 Electrolyte Coatings

Sentencas: With increasing hydrogen flow rate oxide ion conductivity successively decreases.
Titulo: Electrical Properties of Atmospheric Plasma-Sprayed La10(SiO4)6O3 Electrolyte Coatings

Sentencas: The highest ionic conductivity of the dense composite electrolyte coatings reaches a value of 2.4 mS/cm at 900 A degrees C in air, which is comparable to other apatite-type lanthanum silicate (ATLS) conductors.
Titulo: Electrical Properties of Atmospheric Plasma-Sprayed La10(SiO4)6O3 Electrolyte Coatings
